Arc - Class in org.eclipse.gef4.geometry.shapes
Represents the geometric shape of an arc, which is defined by its enclosing framing rectangle, a start angle (relative to the x-axis), and an angular extend (in CCW direction).
Arc(double, double, double, double, Angle, Angle) - Constructor for class org.eclipse.gef4.geometry.shapes.Arc
Constructs a new Arc so that it is fully contained within the framing rectangle defined by (x, y, width, height), spanning the given extend (in CCW direction) from the given start angle (relative to the x-axis).
